00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:27.150
Testament: Acts,

00:02:27.160 --> 00:02:31.589
2 Corinthians 12:2-4, 1

00:02:31.599 --> 00:02:33.350
Thessalonians,

00:02:33.350 --> 00:02:33.360
