00:03:14.550 --> 00:03:14.560
the

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:16.229
transformation that takes place,

00:03:16.239 --> 00:03:18.750
mentioned by the Apostle Paul in 1

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:21.070
Corinthians.

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:24.710
It's so beautiful, I can't

00:03:24.720 --> 00:03:28.710
